metadata.name: #1 Spring Eyes of March
metadata.description:
Spring is a time of renewal, fresh cycles and new beginnings. 

Your spirit is being reawakened after a period of deep stillness and self-reflection. 
You are being reborn. 
You are entering a period of newness after having to face your own darkness. 
You are being regenerated. 
You are rising from within your shadow with a new sense of being. 
You are blooming beloved.

JPEG 6000x4000
300 DPI

Perdika Beach, Lavrion, Greece. March 2018
